overview: The third of five farewell concerts by the 4 remaining members of the Grateful Dead performed on July 3, 2015 in Chicago, IL. SET 1: Tuning, Box Of Rain, Jack Straw, Bertha, Passenger, Technical Difficulties/Tuning, The Wheel, Crazy Fingers, and The Music Never Stopped. SET 2: Tuning, Mason's Children, Scarlet Begonias, Fire On The Mountain, Drum Solo, Space, New Potato Caboose, Playin' In The Band, Let It Grow, Help On The Way, Slipknot!, and Franklin's Tower. ENCORE: Thanks/Phil Donor Rap, and *Ripple.
tagline: What a long strange trip it's been.
title: Grateful Dead: 2015.07.03 - Chicago, IL
